data.description: Wow! Check out this beautifully maintained ranch in quiet, centrally located Virginia Beach neighborhood. Bright and completely open concept. Kitchen has beautiful high end cabinetry, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. No maintenance, scratch-resistant LVP throughout main areas and cushioned carpet in bedrooms. Large sunroom perfect for reading, morning coffee and plants galore! Located close to town center and interstates. Schedule your showing today!
